  "instructions": [
    "Slice stale bread into small cubes and set aside.",
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in shredded carrot, bell pepper, and minced garlic; cook for 4 minutes.",
    "Add sauerkraut and paprika, stirring until well mixed, cook 2 minutes.",
    "Add bread cubes, tossing to coat with the mixture, cook 3 minutes until bread is lightly toasted.",
    "Season with salt, pepper, and lemon juice to taste, cooking for another minute.",
    "Transfer to a plate and serve hot."
  ],
